microphone. It is not a toy.

12:23.493 --> 12:25.577
KNOW-IT-ALL:
Boy, that guy sure likes to show off.

12:25.745 --> 12:28.539
Look what that wise guy
punched on my ticket.

12:28.832 --> 12:35.045
- "L-E." What the heck does that mean?
- Next stop, 11 344 Edbrooke.

12:35.755 --> 12:38.257
