I see him. He's over there.

01:10:15.295 --> 01:10:16.795
I can't see him.

01:10:37.025 --> 01:10:38.984
I can't see him.

01:10:39.152 --> 01:10:41.987
I can't see him!

01:10:46.242 --> 01:10:47.826
[HOOVES CLATTERING]

